# 对象存储服务开发规范

## 存储服务接口

### StorageService 接口

所有存储服务必须实现 [StorageService](mdc:shared/src/commonMain/kotlin/com/xichen/cloudphoto/storage/StorageService.kt) 接口：

```kotlin
interface StorageService {
    suspend fun uploadPhoto(
        config: StorageConfig,
        photoData: ByteArray,
        fileName: String,
        mimeType: String
    ): Result<String> // 返回上传后的 URL
    
    suspend fun deletePhoto(
        config: StorageConfig,
        photoUrl: String
    ): Result<Unit>
    
    suspend fun downloadPhoto(
        config: StorageConfig,
        photoUrl: String
    ): Result<ByteArray>
    
    suspend fun listPhotos(
        config: StorageConfig,
        prefix: String = ""
    ): Result<List<String>>
}
```

## 实现新存储服务

### 1. 添加 Provider 枚举

在 [StorageConfig](mdc:shared/src/commonMain/kotlin/com/xichen/cloudphoto/model/StorageConfig.kt) 中添加：

```kotlin
enum class StorageProvider {
    ALIYUN_OSS,
    AWS_S3,
    TENCENT_COS,
    MINIO,
    CUSTOM_S3,
    NEW_PROVIDER  // 新增
}
```

### 2. 创建实现类

在 `storage/impl/` 目录创建实现类，参考 [AliyunOssService](mdc:shared/src/commonMain/kotlin/com/xichen/cloudphoto/storage/impl/AliyunOssService.kt)：

```kotlin
class NewProviderService(private val httpClient: HttpClient) : StorageService {
    override suspend fun uploadPhoto(
        config: StorageConfig,
        photoData: ByteArray,
        fileName: String,
        mimeType: String
    ): Result<String> {
        return try {
            // 实现上传逻辑
            // 1. 构建签名
            // 2. 构建请求 URL
            // 3. 发送 PUT/POST 请求
            // 4. 返回文件 URL
            Result.success(fileUrl)
        } catch (e: Exception) {
            Result.failure(e)
        }
    }
    
    // 实现其他方法...
}
```

### 3. 注册到工厂

在 [StorageServiceFactory](mdc:shared/src/commonMain/kotlin/com/xichen/cloudphoto/storage/StorageService.kt) 中注册：

```kotlin
object StorageServiceFactory {
    fun create(provider: StorageProvider, httpClient: HttpClient): StorageService {
        return when (provider) {
            // ... 其他 provider
            StorageProvider.NEW_PROVIDER -> NewProviderService(httpClient)
        }
    }
}
```

## 签名算法

### S3 兼容签名

参考 AWS S3 签名算法（HMAC-SHA256）：

```kotlin
// 1. 构建 Canonical Request
val canonicalRequest = buildString {
    append("PUT\n")
    append("/$bucketName/$fileName\n")
    append("\n")
    append("host:$endpoint\n")
    append("\n")
    append("host\n")
    append(sha256Hex(photoData))
}

// 2. 构建 String to Sign
val stringToSign = buildString {
    append("AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\n")
    append("$timestamp\n")
    append("$dateStamp/$region/s3/aws4_request\n")
    append(sha256Hex(canonicalRequest))
}

// 3. 计算签名
val signingKey = getSignatureKey(secretKey, dateStamp, region, "s3")
val signature = hmacSha256(signingKey, stringToSign)
```

### 注意事项

⚠️ **当前实现是简化版本，生产环境需要完善**：
- 支持所有必需的请求头
- 正确处理 URL 编码
- 支持分片上传（大文件）
- 实现签名缓存机制

## 使用存储服务

### 通过 PhotoService

```kotlin
val result = photoService.uploadPhoto(
    photoData = bytes,
    fileName = "photo.jpg",
    mimeType = "image/jpeg",
    width = 1920,
    height = 1080,
    configId = null  // 使用默认配置
)
```

### 直接使用

```kotlin
val config = configRepository.getDefaultConfig()
val storageService = StorageServiceFactory.create(config.provider, httpClient)
val result = storageService.uploadPhoto(config, photoData, fileName, mimeType)
```

## 错误处理

所有方法返回 `Result<T>`，使用 `fold` 处理：

```kotlin
result.fold(
    onSuccess = { url -> /* 成功 */ },
    onFailure = { error -> /* 失败 */ }
)
```

## 支持的存储提供商

- ✅ 阿里云 OSS
- ✅ AWS S3
- ✅ 腾讯云 COS
